Class Climber

  • java.lang.Object
    • Climber

  • public class Climber
extends java.lang.Object
    The objects of the Climber class store and return details about climbers, namely their name, age and gender. Each climber object will also store a list of mountains that have been climbed by the climber.
    Version:
    17/10/2017
    Author:
    Susanne Christensen
